text: in today's world data needs to move fast
but sometimes connectivity limitations
or massive data amounts can prevent your
data from getting to the cloud as
quickly as you need it to introducing
AWS data transfer terminal data transfer
terminals are physical locations around
the world that offer secure personal
Suites equipped with high throughput
upload access to the AWS network with
rapid upload speeds you can move your
data quickly giving your team access to
the information they need sooner getting
started is easy simply search on the AWS
console for the data transfer terminal
location nearest you and make a
reservation for your upload Suite bring
your data with you to your upload Suite
connect your device initiate the upload
and reap the rewards of faster data
transfers data transfer terminal can be
a differentiator for industries that
collect sensor and iot data including
training for Advanced Driver assistance
systems or data collected in remote
locations for scientific research and
development media and entertainment
professionals can benefit too with
accelerated uploads for large files
ensuring timely delivery for post
production processing the uploaded data
can be used for analyzing large data
sets training and running machine
learning models or building scalable
applications using AWS services like
Amazon S3 and Amazon ec2 what's the
weight get your data to the cloud faster
with AWS data transfer terminal
